  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6187115">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6187115/" class="title-link">《心体与性体》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6187115"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/guxueyun/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3124164-13.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/guxueyun/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">白开水</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-07-28"
      class="main-meta">2013-07-28 22:38:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6187115_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  当代新儒家大师牟宗三先生在代表作《心体与性体》中，以其深厚的学养和睿见卓识，在以上诸方面都有精当的判释与论述，并在研究形态与研究方法上树立了中国哲学研究的一个新典范，而这本煌煌一百多万字的巨著，亦被视为研究中国哲学、宋明儒学的经典之作。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            吉林出版集团责任有限公司2013版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
